Author: siu - Chainmakers#3920
Content:
We are happy to announce that on block 200,000 COQUI Cash will do a fork to add Crypto Conditions Smart Contracts capability. This fork will add a fully functional Decentralized Token Exchange, capability to create you own token, a decentralized dice game, capability to create rewards programs and a decentralized faucet. 

Please, if you are running a COQUI full node, update your node as soon as possible to evade a fork on your node. 

The new COQUI Cash execution command looks like this: ./komodod -ac_name=COQUI -ac_supply=72000000 -ac_ccactivate=200000
Questions or suggestions are welcomed,

have a nice day everyone.
